FK, you are quickly becoming that kind of bad sport.  You have agreed with my original point.  There is no loss of face in that.  You're protracting an argument that is moot. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufirion69.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Firion69</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/24/02 4:57:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1035.topic&index=268>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: guns (ot)</span><hr size=1> Guns are not tools. a damn shovel is a tool. you dig with it. The sole purpose of a gun is to kill another human being. That's evil. <p>Master Firion Tar-Estërandir Sorcerer of Vazaelle</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umelcar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>melcar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/24/02 5:27:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1035.topic&index=269>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: guns (ot)</span><hr size=1> Firion69:  So you are saying there are NO legitimate uses for a gun other than to kill?  <br>
