<br>
&quot;After all we did in the 2000 elections, I think we deserve a personal visit from President Bush next year, don't you?&quot; Heston said. The 78-year-old actor then held up an 1874 rifle and reprised a signature line: &quot;From my cold dead hands.&quot; <br>
